[Arduino] the "Serial port monitor" outputs gibberish when run problam
[Arduino] 运行程序时，串口显示器的输出乱码

Question:
the "Serial port monitor" outputs gibberish when run problam
运行程序时，串口显示器的输出乱码

Reason:
when problam with arduino uno, the total RAM is 32k. So is the problam is more than 30k, there has not enough room to run this problem.
使用Arduino uno开发程序时，当程序大小超过30k时，系统就没有足够的空间运行程序了，毕竟uno一共32k内存

Solution:
choose mega2560  of uno
换Mega2560

advice：
when the program is more than 25k, we'd better choose mega 2560
当程序25k+的时候，最好换用mega2560

2017-8-24


